<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śākavarṣē munima<unclear>ṇi</unclear>dinakṛtsaṁmmitē prōṣṭhapadyāṁ sōmāhē puṇyasiddhyai hariśikhari
<lb n="2" break="no"/>pa<unclear>tē</unclear>ranvahaṁ dhūpākālē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pātraśrīpōtarā<unclear>khya</unclear> prabhuvarabhaginī jyāyasī bayyamākhyā prādādā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>caṁdratāraṁ prasavaviracitāmmālikāṁ cāmaraṁ ca <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> tasya rājaladēvīti priyā <unclear>kula</unclear>pālikā svābhī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṣṭasiddhayē prādānnṛharē<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> puṣpamālikāṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> śrī śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1297 gunēṁṭi bha(ṁ)drapāda punna
<lb n="5" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">mi</supplied> sōmavāramunāṁḍu pātrapōtarājiyanaṁgāri Appabayyamadēvi tanaku niṣṭārttha siddhi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>gā śrīnarasi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>hanāthuniki samarppiṁccina cāmara 1 Ī cāmara nityamu<unclear>nnu</unclear> dhūpakālānaṁbaṭṭanu sa 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nula narasisyamokari manumaṟālu tallāsāni saṁpradāyāna tiruvāsāni Arijasānikiṁgā gaṁḍalu
<lb n="8"/>padi māḍalaku reṁḍu kuṁcālu prasādamu ṭhāvapaṭṭi peṭṭenu nityamunnu Oka Ātupaśi tirumāla
<lb n="9"/>peṭṭanu kuṁcaprasādamu ṭhāvupaṭi peṭṭi puṣpavāṭika Oka gaṭu vaḷalāru varadayaṁgāricēta<unclear>pa</unclear><note n="351-1">The continuation of this inscription is covered by a modern wall.</note>
</p>

